{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/install-node-js","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"20ef7b9f-2fe3-53b5-9d0a-4bc754916f53","html":"<p>필자가 자주 사용하는 NodeJS를 설치하는 법을 알아보자!</p>\n<h3 id=\"node-js-설치하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#node-js-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"node js 설치하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Node JS 설치하기</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Window</p>\n<p>윈도우의 경우 <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/ko/download\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">공식 홈페이지</a>에서 msi 파일을 다운받아 설치 할 수 있다. LTS(Long Term Support) 버전과 Current 버전이 있다. Current 버전의 경우 새로운 기술이 도입된 경우가 많은데 이 경우 버그가 많을 수 있다, 따라서 LTS 버전을 설치한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/3dfa7/download_nodejs_window_msi.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.916666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/8ac56/download_nodejs_window_msi.webp 240w,\n/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/d3be9/download_nodejs_window_msi.webp 480w,\n/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/e46b2/download_nodejs_window_msi.webp 960w,\n/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/f992d/download_nodejs_window_msi.webp 1440w,\n/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/882b9/download_nodejs_window_msi.webp 1920w,\n/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/bf558/download_nodejs_window_msi.webp 2028w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/8ff5a/download_nodejs_window_msi.png 240w,\n/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/e85cb/download_nodejs_window_msi.png 480w,\n/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/d9199/download_nodejs_window_msi.png 960w,\n/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/07a9c/download_nodejs_window_msi.png 1440w,\n/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/29114/download_nodejs_window_msi.png 1920w,\n/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/3dfa7/download_nodejs_window_msi.png 2028w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/9845b3a303aebb843d20331ed6bda3d4/d9199/download_nodejs_window_msi.png\"\n            alt=\"download_nodejs_window_msi.png\"\n            title=\"download_nodejs_window_msi.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>설치 후 Node 버전 확인</p>\n<p>터미널을 열고 다음 명령어를 실행한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">C:\\\\~~\\\\user> node -v\nv14.XX.XX</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>MacOS(with linux 계열)</p>\n<p>맥의 경우 NVM을 이용하여 NodeJS를 설치 할 수 있으며 NodeJS 버전 관리도 가능하다. terminal을 열어 다음 명령어를 실행한다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>설치 명령어</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/{버전}/install.sh | bash</code></pre></div>\n<p>버전의 경우 <a href=\"https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">nvm github 페이지</a>에서 확인 할 수 있다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>nvm 설치확인</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ nvm ls\n\n-bash: nvm: command not found # 설치했지만 환경 변수 설정을 안함.</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>vi 또는 사용하는 에디터를 이용</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># bash\n$ vi ~/.bash_profile\n\n# zsh\n$ vi ~/.zshrc</code></pre></div>\n<p>을 입력하여 다음의 텍스트를 입력하고 저장한다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export NVM_DIR=\"$HOME/.nvm\"\n[ -s \"$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh\" ] &amp;&amp; . \"$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh\" # This loads nvm</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>터미널 재실행</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># bash\nsource ~/.bash_profile\n\n# zsh\nssource ~/.zshrc</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>nvm 설치 확인</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ nvm ls\n\n->       system\nnode -> stable (-> N/A) (default)\niojs -> N/A (default)\n... 생략</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Node 설치</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ nvm install --lts</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>설치된 Node 버전 확인</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ nvm ls\n\n->       v14.XX.X\ndefault -> v14.XX.X\nnode -> stable (-> N/A) (default)\niojs -> N/A (default)\n... 생략</code></pre></div>\n<p>설치된 버전이 뜨고 필자는 v14.17.5 버전으로 뜬다</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Node 명령어로 설치된 버전 확인하기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ node -v\nv14.XX.XX</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/install-node-js","tagSlugs":["/tag/node-js/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020/09/20 21:10:00 GMT+0900","description":"NodeJS를 설치해보자!","tags":["NodeJS"],"title":"Node JS 설치하기","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/install-node-js"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}